          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Border Security and Child Safety Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to present to Congress a strategy to ensure the safety of children in the custody of U.S. Customs and Border Protection or U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement, and to prioritize hiring medical personnel to handle the care of such children.<br> </p>]]></text>
